 girdle of the Christian soldier? </div><div class="t m592 x18 h28 y186f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What is to be his breastplate? Whoe righteousness? </div><div class="t m110c x18 h28 y1bbc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">With what are the feet to be shod ? What is to be our&apos; </div><div class="t m12a8 x26 h28 y1727 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shield ? How great is the potency of this shield ? </div><div class="t mdad x18 h28 y16d1 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What protects the seat of the mind? What is the only </div><div class="t m369 x18 h28 y1960 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">weapon of offense or attack? Verses 14-18. </div><div class="t m145 x74 h28 y1b4c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2134 xc5 h28 y16bc ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">With what kind of spirit and conduct must this </div><div class="t m45a x26 h28 y16bd ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">armor be connected to do effectual work ? Who should </div><div class="t m80 x26 h28 y16be ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be included in our supplications? Why did the apostle </div><div class="t mdaf x26 h28 y1d97 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">desire prayers for himself ? What was, then, his situ-</div><div class="t mbda x26 h28 yae9 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ation? How did he desire alwayS to speak? Verses </div><div class="t m691 x26 h28 y1905 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">18-2o. </div><div class="t m148 x74 h28 y174c ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m535 xc5 h28 y1695 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">By whom did he send his epistle? What. was the </div><div class="t me61 x26 h28 y159a ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">character of the messenger? What twofold purpose did </div><div class="t m2f7 x26 h28 yb52 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paul have in sending him? Verses </div><div class="t m16ce x8 he y161e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21, 22. </div><div class="t m14b x73 h28 y1a15 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t mcd0 xc h28 y16a1 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">With what twofold benediction does the epistle </div><div clas